已核对当前 head `059f95b9d76fdbc2d220e31c5b6d47750d1a1d3a`，该问题已修复。`src/datasystem/worker/object_cache/service/worker_oc_service_publish_impl.cpp:431-437` 现在使用 `AccessRecorder::Object(...)` 后的 `ObjectKeyProvider` / `NestedKeyProvider`：

```cpp
auto access = AccessRecorder::Object(AccessRecorderKey::DS_POSIX_PUBLISH);
access.ObjectKeyProvider([&req]() -> std::string { return req.object_key(); })
    .DataSize(req.data_size());
if (req.nested_keys_size() > 0) {
    access.NestedKeyProvider([&req] {
        return objectKeysToString(req.nested_keys());
    });
}
```

`NestedKeyProvider` 只在 `core_.ShouldRecordInternal()` 为 true 时保存 provider，`objectKeysToString(const google::protobuf::RepeatedPtrField<std::string> &)` 只会在 sampled-in 的 `Record()` 阶段执行；sampled-out 不再构造临时 `std::vector<std::string>`，也没有临时 vector 引用悬空的问题。确认标记为已解决。

